@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mbedhw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin((v1 - v2))
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.cos((v0 + 0.54 * v2 + 0.46)))
    v1 = (wp.abs(tmp) * wp.cos((v2 + 0.98 - v1 + 0.71)))
    v0 = 0.70
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.25) - tmp) / ((v2 + 0.34 - v1 + 0.15) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.81)))
    data[tid] = v0
